title: Total Canadian vehicles returning to the country in Canada 2018
summary: The graph shows the trend of the Total Number of Canadian vehicles returning to Canada during the year 2018 .
The Number drops between January and February shows the minimum value in February .
From February on it increases and shows the maximum value in August .
gold: This line graph illustrates the total number of Canadian vehicles that returned to the country in 2018 . The x-axis shows the different months of the year , whereas the y-axis shows the number of vehicles . There is a rise in the first months of the year , reaching a high in August ( 2300000 ) .
